Description: Code Analysis Server (casmgr) — all-in-one containerized MCP server
 Installs a thin systemd unit (casmgr.service) that runs the all-in-one
 casmgr Docker image (PostgreSQL/pgvector + the code-analysis MCP daemon and
 its workers) via `docker compose`. No application code or Python venv runs
 on the host.
 .
 Configuration: /etc/casmgr/config.json, /etc/casmgr/docker-compose.yml
 Data and secrets: /var/casmgr
 Logs: /var/log/casmgr (host) and `docker logs casmgr` / `casmgr logs`
 .
 The Debian package version matches the Docker Hub tag for the casmgr image
 (see /usr/share/casmgr/docker-image and /etc/casmgr/.env after install).
